{"tid":235311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揭秘C919首飛 機師穿救生衣+帶備降傘（有片）","createTime":"2017-05-09T01:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T03:43:56.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dddd354f130ff53d37331f6c22da636fc70f99ee","tid":235311,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T01:59:31.000Z","msg":"中國首架國產大型客機C919日前首飛成功。擔任機長的蔡俊落地後說，首飛機組員全程穿救生衣，艙內還備有降落傘、頭盔，預防飛機出現「根本不可控」的極端情況。<br />\n<br />\n中央電視台報道，C919首飛日期先前一直保密，中國商用飛機公司直到3日才宣布，C919將在5日首飛，若天氣條件不良將順延。5日上午雲層過厚，C919首飛才定在當天下午2時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qy2GalcdLw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQy2GalcdLw8&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a1910aca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qy2GalcdLw8</a><br />\n<br />\n41歲的蔡俊落地後受訪說，首飛前「萬事俱備，就看天氣」。由於首飛具高風險，機組員服裝顏色和配置都與平時訓練不同，「我們其實是背著救生衣的，然後我們機艙裡，還有傘具、頭盔都有」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以防飛機出現不可控狀況</strong><br />\n<br />\n他表示，首飛前考慮到的最極端情況是「飛機根本不可控」，也就是飛行員操縱沒有得到儀器正確回應，控制不了飛機，此時必須選擇緊急逃離。<br />\n<br />\n不過，蔡俊認為這種可能性很微小，因此沒有抱著沉重的心上飛機。畢竟訓練過程中，模擬兩個發動機失效的科目已做了幾十遍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1805000/1805505/t01657c158243aec2a1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1805000%2F1805505%2Ft01657c158243aec2a1_1024.jpg&h=2e30b5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC919首飛五人組。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1805000/1805505/34169981_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1805000%2F1805505%2F34169981_1024.jpg&h=2b9236ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畫面所見，機組人員身穿的原來是救生服。<br />\n<br />\nC919於5日下午2時從上海浦東國際機場起飛，在3000公尺高度巡航飛行79分鐘，並安全返航。由於是首飛，C919未達到一般民航機1萬公尺高空的飛行高度，且全程不收起落架。<br />\n<br />\n蔡俊解釋，首飛以保障安全為主。如果收起落架，可能會收不起或收起後放不下，沒必要承擔這種風險，所以依一般試飛慣例全程未收起落架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1805505?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1805505%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=056f8409\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1805505?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"baadc162f3a14dfabf63908c4642ecf1ef509956","tid":235311,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"死士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a217946ffa6db0f4d2e4ca72242576750ab59c","tid":235311,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"如果救生衣同降落傘都係大陸製就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df6c0141d8c59444544fd2bb007aed4a5f32223","tid":235311,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"試飛不嬲危險，唔單止中國，好正常"},{"pid":"122ea90b2fd19156036cf353171bbc5cd1363934","tid":235311,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"其實好正常姐，美佬一樣會咁"},{"pid":"87c9e1319f5fec33a2396eb1111a85555c4396fa","tid":235311,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"全世界試飛都係橙蛤乸衣加救生衣降落傘<br />\n我都唔知強調基本安全措施既蝗柒定見蝗就打算反既憤青柒"},{"pid":"0a0ee335908b6d5ca99abdcdfbfdd537db0963d7","tid":235311,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"好正常姐, 唔好為笑而笑, 好幼稚<br />\n<br />\n不過希望佢正式首航空中解體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b368e9f12085f3e2c1a7cfecab6d50fa7f5d2978","tid":235311,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"個cockpit好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d2e983b3739877280f77dac9407086d0846c